Xiangyi.

5
00:01:54,780 --> 00:01:55,789
Do you think that

6
00:01:57,539 --> 00:01:59,070
what you say is always right,

7
00:01:59,070 --> 00:02:00,070
always the truth,

8
00:02:00,259 --> 00:02:02,520
and Sigu Sect can't survive without you?

9
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:03,560
Yes.

10
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,640
It has been proven over the years

11
00:02:11,650 --> 00:02:12,980
that all these are true.

12
00:02:13,990 --> 00:02:15,520
Sigu Sect will run normally

13
00:02:16,380 --> 00:02:17,840
regardless of who leaves.

14
00:02:19,220 --> 00:02:20,650
