15
00:02:21,919 --> 00:02:22,850
it'll collapse.

16
00:02:24,030 --> 00:02:24,540
Fine.

17
00:02:30,530 --> 00:02:31,860
You've finally said it.

18
00:02:32,980 --> 00:02:35,180
We grew up together since we were young.

19
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,579
When there was food, I couldn't bear to eat them,

20
00:02:36,579 --> 00:02:37,850
and I gave all of them to you.

21
00:02:37,850 --> 00:02:39,980
I also gave you the best sword I forged.

22
00:02:41,010 --> 00:02:41,980
Deep down,

23
00:02:42,980 --> 00:02:44,260
I value you

24
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:45,260
more than myself.

25
00:02:50,020 --> 00:02:51,079
But what about you?

26
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,329
Since Sigu Sect only needs you,

27
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:02,650
I quit.

28
