♫I asked myself tens of thousands of times♫

33
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:29,190
♫Which moment♫

34
00:03:30,210 --> 00:03:32,840
♫I'd never forget♫

35
00:03:31,900 --> 00:03:32,720
Sect Leader.

36
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:35,870
♫The martial world♫

37
00:03:35,890 --> 00:03:37,490
♫Is so big and fascinating♫

38
00:03:37,510 --> 00:03:39,610
♫We're all wanderers in it♫

39
