♫Is full of aspiring souls♫

43
00:03:50,130 --> 00:03:53,090
♫Let's drink away all our sorrows♫

44
00:03:53,180 --> 00:03:53,760
Senior.

45
00:03:53,350 --> 00:03:58,110
♫Life is like a dream♫

46
00:03:57,579 --> 00:03:58,180
Senior.

47
00:03:58,130 --> 00:04:02,180
♫Our story ends here♫

48
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:10,240
Senior.

49
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:12,990
Senior!

50
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:24,430
Sect Leader.

51
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:26,580
We were ambushed by the Jinyuan Alliance.

52
00:04:26,580 --> 00:04:28,990
Senior's dead body was snatched too.

53
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:33,000
It was a trick of luring the tiger out of the mountain.

54
00:04:33,610 --> 00:04:35,270
Sigu Sect, listen to my order.

55
00:04:35,860 --> 00:04:36,990
From today onwards,

56
00:04:38,050 --> 00:04:39,910
we'll fight the Jinyuan Alliance

57
00:04:40,610 --> 00:04:41,810
till death do us part.

58
00:04:48,670 --> 00:04:49,750
Li Lianhua.

59
00:04:52,020 --> 00:04:53,350
Why are you spacing out?

60
00:04:54,060 --> 00:04:55,650
Since I exposed your nonsense,

61
00:04:55,650 --> 00:04:57,780
you don't know how to quibble anymore, do you?

62
00:04:57,780 --> 00:04:59,510
I can't hide anything from you.

63
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,310
Of course.

64
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:01,909
They are very close.

65
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,690
I'll spare your life today.

66
00:05:03,690 --> 00:05:05,290
Don't spread rumours again.

67
00:05:07,530 --> 00:05:08,390
It's time to go.

68
00:05:17,370 --> 00:05:18,700
Fei knows my uncle.

69
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:20,830
He must know Li Xiangyi.

70
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:25,300
Fei is not familiar with Li Xiangyi.

71
00:05:25,420 --> 00:05:26,820
You don't have to ask him.

72
00:05:27,110 --> 00:05:28,370
I don't care about others,

73
00:05:28,370 --> 00:05:29,970
but I must find out about Fei.

74
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:31,530
He is so bad at martial arts

75
00:05:31,530 --> 00:05:32,460
but so arrogant.

76
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:34,270
There must be something fishy.

77
00:05:34,380 --> 00:05:34,840
Come on.

78
00:05:35,130 --> 00:05:36,410
Let's go to Baichuan Court together.

79
00:05:36,410 --> 00:05:38,340
Why are we going to Baichuan Court?

80
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:40,380
Counting the murder cases in Cailian Manor,

81
00:05:40,380 --> 00:05:42,140
I've already solved three major cases.

82
00:05:42,140 --> 00:05:43,340
It's time to go to Baichuan Court

83
00:05:43,340 --> 00:05:44,810
for the real detective badge.

84
00:05:44,810 --> 00:05:46,730
If so, you will have Baichuan Court as your partner

85
00:05:46,730 --> 00:05:48,330
when you become a detective.

86
00:05:48,970 --> 00:05:50,030
Congratulations.

87
00:05:50,970 --> 00:05:51,830
Same to you.

88
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,720
You used to be my partner,

89
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,560
and you'll also be the only one in the future.

90
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,420
How about this?

91
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:57,960
We'll imitate the Sigu Sect

92
00:05:58,140 --> 00:05:59,600
to solve mysterious cases

93
00:05:59,780 --> 00:06:01,140
and rectify the martial arts world.

94
00:06:01,140 --> 00:06:01,670
Let's go.

95
00:06:07,220 --> 00:06:08,220
So much money?

96
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:09,560
Li Lianhua,

97
00:06:09,980 --> 00:06:10,659
did you strike gold

98
00:06:10,659 --> 00:06:11,460
or get a fever?

99
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,000
You're leaving soon.

100
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:14,340
If you don't prepare well,

101
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:16,100
you may starve to death on the way.

102
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:17,760
Take it to buy some solid food.

103
00:06:18,730 --> 00:06:19,360
No need?

104
00:06:19,540 --> 00:06:21,740
Fine, if you don't need it, I can just...

105
00:06:21,970 --> 00:06:25,230
It's a rare opportunity for misers like you to be generous.

106
00:06:25,410 --> 00:06:27,340
I'll go buy food in town right away.

107
00:06:28,890 --> 00:06:29,490
By the way,

108
00:06:29,910 --> 00:06:30,910
keep an eye on Fei.

109
00:06:31,050 --> 00:06:33,180
I'll investigate him when I come back.

110
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:47,950
I bought a lot of fresh vegetables.

111
00:06:53,630 --> 00:06:54,400
Li Lianhua!

112
00:07:00,170 --> 00:07:01,200
[To Mr. Worried]

113
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:07,700
"Fei and I have personal affairs to attend to.

114
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:08,620
We have to take our leave.

115
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:10,200
So I'm writing this letter to inform you.

116
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:12,530
I'm not leaving without saying goodbye."

117
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:14,030
You cunning old fox.

118
00:07:15,140 --> 00:07:16,340
"I'm not an old fox,

119
00:07:16,370 --> 00:07:17,540
and I'm not cunning at all.

120
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:18,780
This letter is to warn my friend

121
00:07:18,780 --> 00:07:19,900
to stop sulking

122
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:21,340
and leave this place as soon as possible.

123
00:07:21,340 --> 00:07:22,780
Otherwise, things will change."

124
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:24,440
There's no way I will buy that.

125
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,480
"You can surely buy that.

126
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:28,980
Please check it out behind the rock.

127
00:07:31,140 --> 00:07:32,140
I've sent out a smoke signal.

128
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:33,860
Your aunt is coming to catch you.

129
00:07:33,860 --> 00:07:35,620
Leave now."

130
00:07:37,630 --> 00:07:38,290
Li Lianhua,

131
00:07:38,570 --> 00:07:39,450
I hate you!

132
00:07:49,020 --> 00:07:49,550
Hurry up.

133
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:05,250
Director Di,

134
00:08:05,659 --> 00:08:08,460
you've emptied all the pharmacies nearby, right?

135
00:08:08,780 --> 00:08:09,510
Let's begin.

136
00:08:13,890 --> 00:08:15,490
To practice this technique,

137
00:08:15,780 --> 00:08:17,020
you have to insert silver needles at certain anatomical points

138
00:08:17,020 --> 00:08:20,200
and take herbal medicine to get the poison out of your body.

139
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:20,960
Director Di,

140
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:22,410
please meditate and circulate your qi.

141
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:23,720
I'll perform the acupuncture.

142
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,560
Li Xiangyi,

143
00:08:25,020 --> 00:08:28,350
don't play tricks with me when it's related to martial arts.

144
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,080
It's been ten years since we saw each other,

145
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,940
and you've become more vigilant.

146
00:08:32,330 --> 00:08:33,170
Don't worry.

147
00:08:33,390 --> 00:08:34,720
I won't play any tricks.

148
00:08:35,770 --> 00:08:36,700
It would be best.

149
00:08:58,980 --> 00:08:59,940
I've told you

150
00:09:00,420 --> 00:09:01,340
the mantra.

151
00:09:02,170 --> 00:09:04,480
Circulate your inner breath for 49 days,

152
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:07,840
and the poison of the Xiuluo Grass will be detoxified.

153
00:09:08,010 --> 00:09:10,400
Remember, it's 49 days.

154
00:09:11,290 --> 00:09:12,490
Don't miss even a bit.

155
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:22,880
Do you hear me?

156
00:09:23,420 --> 00:09:24,150
Director Di.

157
00:09:25,060 --> 00:09:25,860
Do you hear me?

158
00:09:26,180 --> 00:09:26,910
Director Di.

159
00:09:40,460 --> 00:09:41,520
When should I leave

160
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:42,810
if not now?

161
00:09:47,340 --> 00:09:48,260
My Lord ordered that

162
00:09:48,260 --> 00:09:50,100
I must make Sect Leader Li stay.

163
00:09:51,530 --> 00:09:53,260
Your Lord just said I can leave.

164
00:09:59,420 --> 00:09:59,930
Oh no.

165
00:10:00,740 --> 00:10:02,140
The poisonous grass has backfired on Your Lord.

166
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:03,600
Go quickly and have a look.

167
00:10:20,250 --> 00:10:22,180
You have recovered just like that?

168
00:10:22,220 --> 00:10:25,020
I didn't realize how quickly 49 days went by.

169
00:10:25,650 --> 00:10:26,780
Where are you going?

170
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,050
We're even now.

171
00:10:28,890 --> 00:10:30,120
So I'm leaving.

172
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:32,340
I promised not to expose your identity.

173
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:34,350
But do you think you can retire from the martial arts world

174
00:10:34,350 --> 00:10:35,480
and die like a loser?

175
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:37,700
You're too naive.

176
00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:39,230
Director Di,

177
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:41,720
why bother forcing me?

178
00:10:42,300 --> 00:10:43,900
All I want is for you to live on

179
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:45,750
and fight with me again.

180
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:58,230
Greetings, My Lord.

181
00:10:58,780 --> 00:10:59,710
Medicine Demon.

182
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,320
I want him to regain his inner power.

183
00:11:13,030 --> 00:11:13,670
My Lord,

184
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:15,980
he is severely injured.

185
00:11:16,810 --> 00:11:18,270
It's not easy to deal with.

186
00:11:18,350 --> 00:11:19,150
Is it not easy,

187
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:21,480
or are you not competent enough?

188
00:11:21,970 --> 00:11:22,860
No, no, no.

189
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:26,110
My Lord, if you want him to recover,

190
00:11:26,430 --> 00:11:28,330
I'll try my best.

191
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,990
My Lord, please come with me.

192
00:11:33,770 --> 00:11:34,300
Let's go.

193
00:11:35,450 --> 00:11:35,980
Move.

194
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:47,620
My Lord,

195
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:49,680
Hundreds Herbs Syrup

196
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:52,380
is a treasure I have decocted

197
00:11:52,410 --> 00:11:54,410
with hundreds of exotic herbs for over ten years.

198
00:11:54,410 --> 00:11:56,860
Normally, a cup of it works.

199
00:11:57,260 --> 00:11:58,500
But if you drink too much,

200
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:01,760
your meridians will overreact and cause unbearable pain.

201
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:03,080
Drink that.

202
00:12:08,060 --> 00:12:08,680
Please.

203
00:12:22,550 --> 00:12:23,870
With his injury,

204
00:12:24,330 --> 00:12:26,370
one cup may not work.

205
00:12:26,460 --> 00:12:27,070
Go on.

206
00:12:50,380 --> 00:12:51,540
It's so bitter.

207
00:12:53,930 --> 00:12:54,870
Well...

208
00:12:56,180 --> 00:12:56,830
Feed him.

209
00:12:57,700 --> 00:12:58,430
Yes, My Lord.

210
00:13:04,730 --> 00:13:05,310
Please.

211
00:13:07,270 --> 00:13:07,910
Thank you.

212
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:08,980
I'll do it myself.

213
00:13:24,970 --> 00:13:25,610
My Lord,

214
00:13:26,010 --> 00:13:27,870
this guy's qi has been disrupted.

215
00:13:27,900 --> 00:13:29,230
His inner power is weak.

216
00:13:29,300 --> 00:13:29,760
Well...

217
00:13:29,930 --> 00:13:32,300
Even three cups are of no avail.

218
00:13:36,830 --> 00:13:38,160
His inner power is weak?

219
00:13:44,890 --> 00:13:47,090
I'll insert my inner power into his body

220
00:13:47,930 --> 00:13:49,590
to stimulate the drug effect.

221
00:14:13,850 --> 00:14:14,460
My Lord.

222
00:14:15,060 --> 00:14:16,810
He will die if you do so.

223
00:14:34,980 --> 00:14:36,440
I told you it's incurable.

224
00:14:37,350 --> 00:14:39,010
It's such a waste of resources

225
00:14:39,060 --> 00:14:41,920
for Director Di to get me all these treasures.

226
00:14:43,570 --> 00:14:44,770
Think of another way.

227
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:48,340
Think of a way.

228
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:54,950
We can give it a shot at the Spiritual Snake Cave.

229
00:14:56,910 --> 00:14:58,360
Spiritual Snake Cave?

230
00:15:09,820 --> 00:15:10,460
My Lord,

231
00:15:10,950 --> 00:15:12,580
these spiritual flood dragons in the Eastern Sea

232
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:15,580
have been fed with spiritual medicine for many years.

233
00:15:15,780 --> 00:15:17,930
They like to suck people's qi and feed them again.

234
00:15:17,930 --> 00:15:20,330
Now that this guy's qi is disrupted.

235
00:15:20,490 --> 00:15:23,310
Let's have an exchange transfusion for him.

236
00:15:23,610 --> 00:15:25,610
It might work.

237
00:15:26,770 --> 00:15:27,650
Let's try then.

238
00:15:55,750 --> 00:15:57,780
B-Bicha Poison?

239
00:15:58,280 --> 00:15:58,830
My Lord.

240
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:01,800
He was poisoned by Bicha Poison.

241
00:16:07,340 --> 00:16:07,920
Useless!

242
00:16:09,580 --> 00:16:11,040
My Lord, please calm down.

243
00:16:11,230 --> 00:16:13,430
If you want him to regain his inner power,

244
00:16:13,430 --> 00:16:14,270
and fight him,

245
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:15,710
there's another way.

246
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:16,140
Say it.

247
00:16:16,770 --> 00:16:18,020
Wangchuan Flower.

248
00:16:19,530 --> 00:16:20,590
Wangchuan Flower?

249
00:16:21,860 --> 00:16:23,210
It has the supreme yang.

250
00:16:23,670 --> 00:16:26,670
It can help me break through the eighth level of the Windy Poplar.

251
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:28,750
But his inner power is not strong.

252
00:16:28,930 --> 00:16:29,990
How can it cure him?

253
00:16:32,410 --> 00:16:33,400
My Lord,

254
00:16:33,700 --> 00:16:36,540
Wangchuan Flower has two different types, namely Yin and Yang.

255
00:16:36,540 --> 00:16:39,370
The Yang grass is a kind of martial art, same as you.

256
00:16:39,740 --> 00:16:40,770
While the Yin grass

257
00:16:40,770 --> 00:16:42,900
is the most poisonous grass in the world.

258
00:16:42,900 --> 00:16:44,760
Even if a child takes it,

259
00:16:44,950 --> 00:16:47,810
they can gain more than ten years of martial skills.

260
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:50,260
But it's like the last radiance of the setting sun.

261
00:16:50,260 --> 00:16:51,540
A few days later,

262
00:16:51,780 --> 00:16:53,870
the Yin grass will start to have a strong effect,

263
00:16:53,870 --> 00:16:55,400
and it will get stronger and stronger.

264
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:57,140
His meridians will break

265
00:16:57,180 --> 00:16:58,550
and his organs will split.

266
00:16:58,550 --> 00:17:01,710
There is no other way to die more terribly

267
00:17:01,740 --> 00:17:03,980
than it in the world.

268
00:17:04,180 --> 00:17:06,110
I don't want him to live a long life.

269
00:17:06,520 --> 00:17:08,820
I just want him to live on until we fight again.

270
00:17:08,820 --> 00:17:09,460
Let's go.

271
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:12,300
I want the Wangchuan Flower.

272
00:17:12,970 --> 00:17:14,400
Yes, My Lord.

273
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:27,220
Why are you laughing?

274
00:17:28,220 --> 00:17:28,950
Director Di,

275
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:31,980
stop wasting your time.

276
00:17:32,859 --> 00:17:34,220
It's all for nothing.

277
00:17:35,220 --> 00:17:37,650
So what if you get the Wangchuan Flower?

278
00:17:38,339 --> 00:17:39,770
You can force me to eat it,

279
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,700
but you can't force me to fight with you.

280
00:17:42,700 --> 00:17:44,540
By then, I'll lie in front of you

281
00:17:44,620 --> 00:17:46,420
and wait for death under the sun,

282
00:17:46,620 --> 00:17:47,750
