00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,240
Don't get choked.

563
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:38,880
I'm not eating.

564
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:39,340
You eat.

565
00:33:40,100 --> 00:33:41,500
Why are you staring at me?

566
00:33:44,900 --> 00:33:45,740
It's nothing.

567
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:48,820
Aren't you more like your mother?

568
00:33:51,100 --> 00:33:52,900
What kind of nonsense is that?

569
00:33:53,290 --> 00:33:54,530
Our butler said

570
00:33:54,800 --> 00:33:56,700
I resemble my second aunt the most.

571
00:33:56,700 --> 00:33:57,760
But when I was born,

572
00:33:57,890 --> 00:33:59,690
my second aunt had already died.

573
00:34:04,380 --> 00:34:06,510
You didn't see your uncles many times.

574
00:34:06,940 --> 00:34:08,070
When you were young,

575
00:34:09,040 --> 00:34:10,340
did he dote on you much?

576
00:34:10,900 --> 00:34:13,230
My uncle is the second master of the Sigu Sect.

577
00:34:13,230 --> 00:34:14,440
He was usually very busy.

578
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,900
He didn't have time for me.

579
00:34:16,140 --> 00:34:18,800
Besides, my mother seemed to hate him very much.

580
00:34:19,130 --> 00:34:21,260
She didn't allow me to get close to him.

581
00:34:26,659 --> 00:34:29,260
Why do you suddenly ask about my family matter?

582
00:34:30,659 --> 00:34:31,460
It's nothing.

583
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:33,280
I was just asking.

584
00:34:33,900 --> 00:34:34,830
Eat your buns.

585
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:39,060
Then let me ask you.

586
00:34:39,420 --> 00:34:41,150
You have to answer me honestly.

587
00:34:41,540 --> 00:34:43,469
Who is Fei exactly?

588
00:34:43,860 --> 00:34:45,860
Why is he so skilful in martial arts?

589
00:34:47,530 --> 00:34:49,190
Since we are now at this point,

590
00:34:49,199 --> 00:34:51,000
I won't hide it from you anymore.

591
00:34:51,210 --> 00:34:52,290
He's Di Feisheng.

592
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:56,159
D-Di Feisheng?

593
00:34:56,889 --> 00:34:59,100
The devil of the Jinyuan Alliance, Di Feisheng?

594
00:34:59,100 --> 00:34:59,560
Well...

595
00:35:00,980 --> 00:35:02,260
Do you know my master

596
00:35:02,260 --> 00:35:04,170
is unaccounted for ten years because of him?

597
00:35:04,170 --> 00:35:06,230
How can you hang out with such a devil?

598
00:35:08,180 --> 00:35:09,990
He asked me to promise him to save someone.

599
00:35:09,990 --> 00:35:10,790
Save someone?

600
00:35:11,460 --> 00:35:13,100
You can lie with your medical skills,

601
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:14,900
but you can't save lives with it.

602
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:18,400
There are people in this world

603
00:35:19,390 --> 00:35:20,850
who can only be saved by me.

604
00:35:22,050 --> 00:35:22,980
Unfortunately,

605
00:35:24,300 --> 00:35:25,700
I don't want to save them.

606
00:35:25,780 --> 00:35:27,180
So you left me behind

607
00:35:27,910 --> 00:35:30,120
because you were afraid Di Feisheng would deal with me,

608
00:35:30,120 --> 00:35:31,090
but it turned out that you were caught

609
00:35:31,090 --> 00:35:32,740
and got hurt all over your body.

610
00:35:32,740 --> 00:35:33,400
Li Lianhua,

611
00:35:33,610 --> 00:35:34,980
I won't accept your kindness for that.

612
00:35:34,980 --> 00:35:36,850
We agreed that friends should share weal and woe.

613
00:35:36,850 --> 00:35:38,850
Even if the opponent is Di Feisheng.

614
00:35:42,110 --> 00:35:43,040
Young Hero Fang,

615
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:44,540
I know you're good.

616
00:35:45,010 --> 00:35:46,340
It's my fault this time.

617
00:35:46,710 --> 00:35:47,310
Thank you.

618
00:35:47,770 --> 00:35:49,500
At least you have a conscience.

619
00:35:49,540 --> 00:35:50,140
By the way,

620
00:35:50,340 --> 00:35:51,820
don't promise Di Feisheng

621
00:35:52,160 --> 00:35:53,730
to save the person he mentioned.

622
00:35:53,730 --> 00:35:54,910
The person he wants to save

623
00:35:54,910 --> 00:35:56,710
is definitely not a good person.

624
00:35:58,140 --> 00:35:59,800
He is indeed not a good person.

625
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:01,960
I won't save him.

626
00:36:02,730 --> 00:36:04,590
It's more important to save you now.

627
00:36:04,590 --> 00:36:05,450
Di Feisheng has inserted Gang Qi

628
00:36:05,450 --> 00:36:07,360
into your body.

629
00:36:08,060 --> 00:36:09,320
It'll be troublesome.

630
00:36:11,180 --> 00:36:11,990
It doesn't matter.

631
00:36:11,990 --> 00:36:13,260
I'm talented.

632
00:36:13,660 --> 00:36:14,960
I felt a little uncomfortable just now.

633
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:15,560
Look now.

634
00:36:15,850 --> 00:36:16,830
I'm fine.

635
00:36:41,510 --> 00:36:43,380
I don't have much inner power left.

636
00:36:43,380 --> 00:36:46,190
I almost can't deploy my power to suppress the Gang Qi.

637
00:36:46,190 --> 00:36:48,190
But if Gang Qi reaches his temple,

638
00:36:49,020 --> 00:36:50,080
he will surely die.

639
00:36:50,890 --> 00:36:52,020
This is the only way.

640
00:36:58,400 --> 00:36:59,200
You're awake.

641
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:06,420
Get up and have some warm water.

642
00:37:08,680 --> 00:37:09,880
Why did I faint again?

643
00:37:11,150 --> 00:37:12,290
You've been inserted Gang Qi.

644
00:37:12,290 --> 00:37:13,820
You fainted all of a sudden.

645
00:37:14,770 --> 00:37:16,070
I didn't expect that you are so heavy

646
00:37:16,070 --> 00:37:17,530
that I was exhausted

647
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:19,880
to carry you back to the Lotus Tower.

648
00:37:23,870 --> 00:37:27,470
Practice the skill set according to the papers I put on the table.

649
00:37:27,780 --> 00:37:29,040
Practice it properly.

650
00:37:39,050 --> 00:37:39,780
What is this?

651
00:37:40,530 --> 00:37:41,230
A draft?

652
00:37:43,100 --> 00:37:43,870
A draft?

653
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:46,410
This is an ancestral skill.

654
00:37:46,980 --> 00:37:47,710
Previously,

655
00:37:47,790 --> 00:37:49,000
the Gang Qi inside your body

656
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:50,390
was suppressed by it.

657
00:37:50,990 --> 00:37:51,870
Study hard.

658
00:37:52,140 --> 00:37:53,710
Don't bother me anymore.

659
00:37:55,090 --> 00:37:56,370
It's ancestral?

660
00:37:57,030 --> 00:37:58,480
The ink is not dry yet.

661
00:37:58,930 --> 00:38:00,260
Did you draw it just now?

662
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:02,450
The ancestral martial arts

663
00:38:02,460 --> 00:38:04,140
must be passed down by word of mouth.

664
00:38:04,140 --> 00:38:05,330
So I drew it for you

665
00:38:05,370 --> 00:38:06,630
to make you understand

666
00:38:06,740 --> 00:38:07,600
and learn well.

667
00:38:07,830 --> 00:38:08,560
Understand?

668
00:38:09,530 --> 00:38:11,470
I can't simply practice any martial arts for no reason.

669
00:38:11,470 --> 00:38:12,780
If it can't cure the Gang Qi,

670
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:13,760
and I'm obsessed because of it,

671
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:14,650
it's not worth it.

672
00:38:14,650 --> 00:38:15,740
I won't practice it.

673
00:38:15,740 --> 00:38:16,110
No.

674
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:20,130
Do you know why Di Feisheng

675
00:38:21,500 --> 00:38:22,830
wanted me to save lives?

676
00:38:24,210 --> 00:38:25,940
It's because of this skill set.

677
00:38:26,170 --> 00:38:27,370
If you don't trust me,

678
00:38:27,560 --> 00:38:29,000
or you doubt me, it's fine.

679
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:30,530
But Di Feisheng's judgment

680
00:38:30,820 --> 00:38:31,800
can't be wrong.

681
00:38:34,580 --> 00:38:35,470
You don't want it?

682
00:38:35,470 --> 00:38:36,930
Fine, if you don't want it, give it to me.

683
00:38:36,930 --> 00:38:37,660
Give it to me.

684
00:38:40,540 --> 00:38:41,820
Listen, Fang Xiaobao,

685
00:38:42,090 --> 00:38:43,550
how can you be a detective?

686
00:38:43,750 --> 00:38:45,310
You're such a fool,

687
00:38:45,330 --> 00:38:45,860
an idiot.

688
00:38:45,870 --> 00:38:46,990
How can you be a detective?

689
00:38:46,990 --> 00:38:48,430
Can't you think about

690
00:38:48,540 --> 00:38:49,850
why Di Feisheng

691
00:38:50,010 --> 00:38:51,750
used you to threaten me to save others?

692
00:38:51,750 --> 00:38:54,350
If the Gang Qi in your body is getting more serious,

693
00:38:54,350 --> 00:38:55,990
you'll fall into his trap

694
00:38:56,620 --> 00:38:58,150
because you have to listen to him.

695
00:38:58,150 --> 00:38:59,480
What should you do then?

696
00:38:59,520 --> 00:39:01,000
That devil keeps killing people

697
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:01,860
and keeps doing evil.

698
00:39:01,860 --> 00:39:03,120
Don't you feel guilty?

699
00:39:03,250 --> 00:39:04,510
-Do you want to practice it or not?
-Fine.

700
00:39:04,510 --> 00:39:05,180
I will practice it.

701
00:39:05,180 --> 00:39:06,050
You're talking too much.

702
00:39:06,050 --> 00:39:07,710
I won't let the devil succeed.

703
00:39:08,050 --> 00:39:08,960
Remember.

704
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:10,200
If I

705
00:39:10,570 --> 00:39:12,010
go crazy,

706
00:39:12,030 --> 00:39:12,660
foam at the mouth

707
00:39:12,660 --> 00:39:14,060
and dance uncontrollably after practising it,

708
00:39:14,060 --> 00:39:16,270
do remember to find me a physician from the town.

709
00:39:16,270 --> 00:39:17,000
Don't worry.

710
00:39:17,610 --> 00:39:20,410
I'll get you any expensive medicine if you need it.

711
00:39:20,850 --> 00:39:21,710
Practice hard.

712
00:39:24,460 --> 00:39:25,300
Fine.

713
00:39:50,420 --> 00:39:51,660
After all, you've called Li Xiangyi

714
00:39:51,660 --> 00:39:53,320
your master for so many years.

715
00:39:53,690 --> 00:39:55,690
I'll pass this Yangzhouman to you.

716
00:39:56,890 --> 00:39:59,840
It's a way to repay his promise to you.

717
00:40:28,260 --> 00:40:29,320
What are you doing?

718
00:40:29,680 --> 00:40:31,280
Are you sleepwalking at night?

719
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:31,940
Li Lianhua,

720
00:40:32,660 --> 00:40:34,460
where did you get that skill set?

721
00:40:34,580 --> 00:40:35,580
Didn't I tell you?

722
00:40:35,620 --> 00:40:36,500
It's ancestral.

723
00:40:36,500 --> 00:40:37,230
Impossible.

724
00:40:38,210 --> 00:40:39,560
The skill set is profound and mysterious.

725
00:40:39,560 --> 00:40:40,560
It's very useful.

726
00:40:40,780 --> 00:40:42,580
Even Tianji Hall's Mind-reading Skills

727
00:40:42,580 --> 00:40:43,710
can't compare to it.

728
00:40:44,370 --> 00:40:45,830
If it's really ancestral,

729
00:40:46,150 --> 00:40:49,540
there must have been many high-skilled warriors coming from your family.

730
00:40:49,540 --> 00:40:50,100
Tell me.

731
00:40:50,700 --> 00:40:51,830
Where did you get it?

732
00:40:52,590 --> 00:40:53,590
Let go of me!

733
00:40:54,200 --> 00:40:54,860
No manners.

734
00:40:57,670 --> 00:40:58,050
Fine.

735
00:40:59,220 --> 00:41:01,950
One year, I went to the mountain to collect herbs.

736
00:41:02,340 --> 00:41:04,400
Unfortunately, I fell off the cliff.

737
00:41:04,820 --> 00:41:06,890
Suddenly, in front of a cave,

738
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:08,720
a fairy godmother appeared.

739
00:41:09,050 --> 00:41:10,980
She asked me to kowtow thrice to her

740
00:41:11,430 --> 00:41:13,240
and passed me the set of skills.

741
00:41:13,890 --> 00:41:15,410
After thinking about it,

742
00:41:15,820 --> 00:41:18,820
I realised that was a legendary immortal fate.

743
00:41:19,930 --> 00:41:20,430
Bah!

744
00:41:21,250 --> 00:41:23,380
How can there be like the pie in the sky?

745
00:41:23,380 --> 00:41:24,280
Didn't I tell you?

746
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:25,410
It's all fate.

747
00:41:25,830 --> 00:41:26,550
Tell me

748
00:41:27,040 --> 00:41:28,840
what the name of the skill set is.

749
00:41:29,260 --> 00:41:30,190
That's amazing.

750
00:41:31,010 --> 00:41:32,590
It's almost the same as Yangzhouman.

751
00:41:32,590 --> 00:41:33,590
It's Suzhoukuai.

752
00:41:34,730 --> 00:41:35,860
I'm not buying that.

753
00:41:37,200 --> 00:41:38,480
You know what?

754
00:41:38,610 --> 00:41:40,460
You asked me to tell you, but you don't believe me after I told you.

755
00:41:40,460 --> 00:41:41,620
Then explain to me

756
00:41:42,230 --> 00:41:44,080
why I, a physician who sells plasters,

757
00:41:44,080 --> 00:41:45,860
can get the ultimate skill set.

758
00:41:51,380 --> 00:41:53,380
If I were born good at martial arts,

759
00:41:53,710 --> 00:41:55,170
I would have become a hero.

760
00:41:56,300 --> 00:41:57,230
Unfortunately,

761
00:41:57,380 --> 00:41:58,780
we have different fates.

762
00:41:59,130 --> 00:42:01,130
I can only be a wandering physician.

763
00:42:01,580 --> 00:42:02,540
Unlike someone,

764
00:42:03,080 --> 00:42:04,810
who's going to be a master soon.

765
00:42:05,870 --> 00:42:06,480
All right.

766
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:09,010
I owe you this time.

767
00:42:11,770 --> 00:42:13,680
It's okay if you don't know martial arts.

768
00:42:13,680 --> 00:42:14,880
It's the same if I can.

769
00:42:15,510 --> 00:42:17,580
After we get out of here, I'll take care of you

770
00:42:17,580 --> 00:42:18,500
and protect you.

771
00:42:18,500 --> 00:42:20,250
No matter what happens, just mention my name.

772
00:42:20,250 --> 00:42:21,310
Most importantly,

773
00:42:22,500 --> 00:42:24,110
I kowtowed three times

774
00:42:24,580 --> 00:42:25,710
to get the skill set.

775
00:42:25,930 --> 00:42:27,900
So you also have to kowtow thrice to me

776
00:42:27,900 --> 00:42:29,430
so that I can feel better.

777
00:42:31,490 --> 00:42:32,280
Dream on.

778
00:42:32,640 --> 00:42:33,540
Except for my parents,

779
00:42:33,540 --> 00:42:35,390
I'll only kowtow to my master, Li Xiangyi.

780
00:42:35,390 --> 00:42:36,150
Who are you?

781
00:42:36,540 --> 00:42:37,580
Your Suzhoukuai

782
00:42:37,900 --> 00:42:40,900
is definitely not as good as my master's Yangzhouman.

783
00:42:41,380 --> 00:42:42,270
Take your time.

784
00:42:42,840 --> 00:42:43,500
Li Lianhua,

785
00:42:43,760 --> 00:42:44,470
why don't you tell me more

786
00:42:44,470 --> 00:42:45,470
about my master?

787
00:42:45,630 --> 00:42:46,580
You said too little last time.

788
00:42:46,580 --> 00:42:47,460
I haven't heard enough yet.

789
00:42:47,460 --> 00:42:48,950
Don't you feel hot

790
00:42:48,980 --> 00:42:50,180
and chest tightness?

791
00:42:50,850 --> 00:42:51,310
No.

792
00:42:51,530 --> 00:42:53,930
The crucial part of Suzhoukuai is silence.

793
00:42:54,620 --> 00:42:55,950
Most importantly, talk less

794
00:42:55,950 --> 00:42:56,680
and be quiet.

795
00:42:56,740 --> 00:42:58,440
When you talk, you'll spend your energy and cause blood flow.

796
00:42:58,440 --> 00:43:00,170
It'll boom like a firecracker.

797
00:43:00,230 --> 00:43:01,270
It's up to you.

